transform.filter: ((datum.a + dii_floor + max_one_side_tiles_count) % max_one_side_tiles_count) >= 0 && (datum.b + djj_floor) >= 0 && ((datum.a + dii_floor + max_one_side_tiles_count) % max_one_side_tiles_count) <= (max_one_side_tiles_count - 1) && (datum.b + djj_floor) <= (max_one_side_tiles_count - 1)

params.name: djj
params.expr: (1 - log(tan(base_point[1] * PI / 180) + 1 / cos(base_point[1] * PI / 180)) / PI) / 2 * max_one_side_tiles_count
